    <div class="package-grid reveal">
      <div class="pkg-card">
        <div class="pkg-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1537996194471-e657df975ab4?w=600&q=80" alt="Bali" /></div>
        <div class="pkg-body">
          <h4>Bali Romantic Escape — 5N/6D</h4>
          <p>Ubud rice terraces, Tanah Lot, Seminyak beach clubs, private villa, cooking class.</p>
          <div class="pkg-meta"><span>📅 5 Nights</span><span>🌅 Private Villa</span></div>
