      <div class="section-tag">Southeast Asia</div>
      <h2 class="section-title"><span>Thailand</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Bangkok's temples, Phuket's turquoise waters, Chiang Mai's elephants, and the legendary Thai cuisine.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="package-grid reveal">
      <div class="pkg-card">
        <div class="pkg-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506665531195-3566af2b4dfa?w=600&q=80" alt="Thailand" /></div>
        <div class="pkg-body">
          <h4>Thailand Classic — 6N/7D</h4>
          <p>Bangkok temple tour, Phi Phi islands, Phuket beach, Thai cooking class, elephant sanctuary.</p>
          <div class="pkg-meta"><span>📅 6 Nights</span><span>🏄 Island Hopping</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="pkg-footer">
          <div class="pkg-price">₹40,000<small>per person</small></div>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding:10px 20px;font-size:13px;">Enquire</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Vietnam -->
  <div id="vietnam">
    <div class="section-header center reveal">
      <div class="section-tag">Southeast Asia</div>
      <h2 class="section-title"><span>Vietnam</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Ha Long Bay's limestone karsts, Hoi An's lantern-lit streets, Ho Chi Minh City's energy, and world-class cuisine.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="package-grid reveal">
      <div class="pkg-card">
        <div class="pkg-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555921015-5532091f6026?w=600&q=80" alt="Vietnam" /></div>
        <div class="pkg-body">
          <h4>Vietnam Explorer — 7N/8D</h4>
          <p>Ha Long Bay cruise, Hoi An lantern festival, Hue Imperial Citadel, Da Nang beaches.</p>
          <div class="pkg-meta"><span>📅 7 Nights</span><span>⛵ Bay Cruise</span></div>
